org.jmisb.api.klv.st0102

Class SecurityMetadataString

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0102.SecurityMetadataString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, ISecurityMetadataValue

    public class SecurityMetadataString
extends Object
implements ISecurityMetadataValue
    Represents a string value in ST 0102.

    Strings are used across a range of security metadata items. This class represents the various kinds of strings.
